[{"data":1,"prerenderedAt":576},["ShallowReactive",2],{"header-locale:\u002Fvscode\u002F20240908\u002F3488366595\u002F":3,"page:\u002Fvscode\u002F20240908\u002F3488366595\u002F":4,"alt:\u002Fvscode\u002F20240908\u002F3488366595\u002F":3,"prev-next:\u002Fvscode\u002F20240908\u002F3488366595\u002F":552,"related:\u002Fvscode\u002F20240908\u002F3488366595\u002F":561},"\u002Fen\u002Fvscode\u002F2024\u002F09\u002F08\u002Fgithub-copilot-tips-and-tricks-deep-dive\u002F",{"id":5,"title":6,"abbrlink":7,"altUrl":3,"body":8,"category":537,"date":538,"description":25,"extension":255,"lang":539,"meta":540,"navigation":322,"path":541,"readingMinutes":542,"seo":543,"standalone":544,"stem":545,"tags":546,"tldr":549,"updated":538,"url":550,"__hash__":551},"content\u002FVSCode\u002FGitHub-Copilot-技巧全攻略不藏私！.md","GitHub Copilot 好難用？說不定是你不懂 Copilot 之技巧全攻略不藏私！","3488366595",{"type":9,"value":10,"toc":515},"minimark",[11,19,23,26,30,33,36,43,46,53,67,71,74,81,96,99,104,107,112,133,137,144,150,153,160,164,167,170,175,184,189,192,198,209,214,219,226,230,241,247,250,267,272,275,281,284,290,296,300,303,306,337,345,351,355,358,364,368,371,377,380,386,389,395,403,409,416,423,426,431,434,439,445,452,455,460,466,473,484,490,495,505,508,511],[12,13,14],"p",{},[15,16],"img",{"alt":17,"src":18},"GitHub Copilot","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002Fblog\u002Fvscode\u002Fgithub-copilot\u002F68747470733a2f2f7265732e636c6f7564696e6172792e636f6d2f70726163746963616c6465762f696d6167652f66657463682f732d2d70454d3650587a582d2d2f635f696d616767615f7363616c652c665f6175746f2c666c5f70726f67726573736976652c685f3432302c715f6175746f2c775f313030302f687.webp",[20,21,22],"h2",{"id":22},"前言",[12,24,25],{},"身為用了 GitHub Copilot 一陣子的使用者，這一篇我將會分享一些我使用 GitHub Copilot 的心得與技巧，讓大家開發時更加得心應手，那麼廢話就不多說，我們來聊聊 GitHub Copilot 吧！",[20,27,29],{"id":28},"什麼是-github-copilot","什麼是 GitHub Copilot？",[12,31,32],{},"首先這邊要說明一下 GitHub Copilot 跟 Copilot 是兩種東西，Copilot 是指 Microsoft Copilot 而非 GitHub Copilot，這邊我們要講的是 GitHub Copilot。",[12,34,35],{},"那麼為什麼會特別提到這件事情呢？因為原本 Microsoft Copilot 是叫做「Bing AI」，但某一天 Microsoft 決定改叫 Copilot，這樣就會跟 GitHub Copilot 有點混淆，所以這邊才特別說明一下，避免大家搞混。",[12,37,38,39],{},"而本文因為會有簡寫，",[40,41,42],"strong",{},"所以在本文所提到的 Copilot 就是 GitHub Copilot 而非 Microsoft Copilot 唷！",[12,44,45],{},"回頭講一下 Copilot 到底是什麼東西，簡單來講 Copilot 是一個由 GitHub 與 OpenAI 合作開發的 AI 程式，透過放在 GitHub 上的開源程式碼所訓練出來的 AI 模型，讓開發者們在撰寫程式碼時可以更快速的完成程式碼。",[12,47,48,49,52],{},"那麼由於軟體更新速度非常快速，所以這邊我要特別標記一下，本文是基於 ",[40,50,51],{},"2024 年 9 月的 GitHub 1.229.0 版本","所撰寫的，所以如果有任何更新的功能或是變動，請以 GitHub 官方文件為主唷！",[54,55,56],"blockquote",{},[12,57,58,61,62,66],{},[40,59,60],{},"Note","\n其實 GitHub Copilot 的定位是「",[63,64,65],"code",{},"Pair programming（結隊開發）","」，Pair programming 的意思是說，兩個人一起開發，其中一個人是主要的開發者，另一個人是幫忙的開發者，而 Copilot 就是幫忙的開發者，只是從人類換成了 AI 而已，透過 AI 的幫助，讓開發者可以更快速的完成程式碼。\n所以 GitHub 中文又稱 GitHub 副駕駛。",[20,68,70],{"id":69},"安裝-github-copilot","安裝 GitHub Copilot",[12,72,73],{},"安裝方式非常簡單，只需要在 Visual Studio Code 的擴充功能商店搜尋「GitHub Copilot」，然後點選安裝即可。",[54,75,76],{},[12,77,78,80],{},[40,79,60],{},"\nCopilot 不止支援 Visual Studio Code，也支援其他的編輯器，例如：Microsoft Visual Studio、Vim、Cursor 或 JetBrains，但這邊會著重於 Visual Studio Code。",[12,82,83,84,90,91],{},"你會找到兩個擴充功能，一個是 ",[85,86,17],"a",{"href":87,"rel":88},"https:\u002F\u002Fmarketplace.visualstudio.com\u002Fitems?itemName=GitHub.copilot",[89],"nofollow","，另一個是 ",[85,92,95],{"href":93,"rel":94},"https:\u002F\u002Fmarketplace.visualstudio.com\u002Fitems?itemName=GitHub.copilot-chat",[89],"GitHub Copilot Chat",[12,97,98],{},"不論你安裝哪一個，兩者都會一起安裝，所以你可以選擇安裝哪一個都可以，一個是 Copilot 的主要套件，另一個是 Copilot 的聊天室",[12,100,101],{},[15,102],{"alt":17,"src":103},"https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002Fblog\u002Fvscode\u002Fgithub-copilot\u002F%E6%88%AA%E5%9C%96%202024-09-08%2013.33.12.png",[12,105,106],{},"安裝完成後，你會看到 Visual Studio Code 的右下角會出現一個 Copilot 的圖示以及左側的 Copilot 聊天室",[12,108,109],{},[15,110],{"alt":17,"src":111},"https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002Fblog\u002Fvscode\u002Fgithub-copilot\u002F%E5%85%A8%E7%86%92%E5%B9%95_2024_9_8_13_36.jpg",[54,113,114],{},[12,115,116,118,119,122,123,126,127,132],{},[40,117,60],{},"\nGitHub Copilot 是付費的擴充功能，一年約 ",[63,120,121],{},"100"," 美金（相當於台幣約 ",[63,124,125],{},"3000"," 元），但如果你是學生的話，你可以透過 ",[85,128,131],{"href":129,"rel":130},"https:\u002F\u002Fisraynotarray.com\u002Fother\u002F20201102\u002F32425\u002F",[89],"GitHub Education"," 來免費使用唷！",[20,134,136],{"id":135},"github-copilot-的使用","GitHub Copilot 的使用",[12,138,139,140,143],{},"基本上，你只要寫程式碼時，Copilot 就會自動幫你完成程式碼，而且 Copilot 並不局限於程式碼的部分，包含我在寫這篇文章時，Copilot 也會幫我往後面產生一些文字，幫我預測我預計要打的文字是什麼，然後你只需要按下 ",[63,141,142],{},"Tab"," 鍵就可以完成程式碼。",[12,145,146],{},[15,147],{"alt":148,"src":149},"Copilot 預測","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002Fblog\u002Fvscode\u002Fgithub-copilot\u002FSep-08-2024%2013-41-26.gif",[12,151,152],{},"而這個是 GitHub Copilot 的基本功能，但 Copilot 還有很多其他的功能，這邊我們來看看一些 Copilot 的技巧。",[54,154,155],{},[12,156,157,159],{},[40,158,60],{},"\nGitHub Copilot 會以你開啟的工作區（Workspace）來訓練 Copilot，因此程式碼的品質會依照你的工作區來訓練並生成。",[161,162,163],"h3",{"id":163},"註解產生程式碼",[12,165,166],{},"前面有簡單展示了一下 Copilot 可以自動幫我們預測後面要打的內容，但 Copilot 還有一個很厲害的功能，就是透過註解來產生程式碼！",[12,168,169],{},"而這功能很簡單，你只需要寫好註解，然後讓 Copilot 幫你產生程式碼即可，例如：",[12,171,172],{},[15,173],{"alt":163,"src":174},"https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002Fblog\u002Fvscode\u002Fgithub-copilot\u002FSep-08-2024%2013-53-04.gif",[12,176,177,178,183],{},"如果上方我使用了 ",[85,179,182],{"href":180,"rel":181},"https:\u002F\u002Fisraynotarray.com\u002Fjavascript\u002F20230513\u002F284079926\u002F",[89],"JSDoc"," 來撰寫註解，然後 Copilot 就會自動幫我產生程式碼，這樣就可以讓我們更快速的完成程式碼，如果你只是單純寫註解也可以",[12,185,186],{},[15,187],{"alt":163,"src":188},"https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002Fblog\u002Fvscode\u002Fgithub-copilot\u002FSep-08-2024%2013-55-23.gif",[12,190,191],{},"如果你不滿意這個結果時，有時候你可以滑鼠移動過去選取其他預測結果",[12,193,194],{},[15,195],{"alt":196,"src":197},"預測結果","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002Fblog\u002Fvscode\u002Fgithub-copilot\u002F%E6%88%AA%E5%9C%96%202024-09-08%2015.25.32.png",[12,199,200,201,204,205,208],{},"如果你發現就算點了下一頁看其他預測結果也不滿意的話，你可以點「",[63,202,203],{},"...","」並找到 ",[63,206,207],{},"Open Completions Panel"," 來查看更多可能的預測結果",[12,210,211],{},[15,212],{"alt":207,"src":213},"https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002Fblog\u002Fvscode\u002Fgithub-copilot\u002F%E6%88%AA%E5%9C%96%202024-09-08%2015.26.38.png",[12,215,216],{},[15,217],{"alt":207,"src":218},"https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002Fblog\u002Fvscode\u002Fgithub-copilot\u002F%E6%88%AA%E5%9C%96%202024-09-08%2015.26.51.png",[12,220,221,222,225],{},"若有滿意的，你只需要點「",[63,223,224],{},"Accept Suggestion（接受建議）","」即可。",[161,227,229],{"id":228},"指令呼叫-copilot-撰寫程式碼","指令呼叫 Copilot 撰寫程式碼",[12,231,232,233,236,237,240],{},"如果你不想要在檔案中保留\u002F撰寫註解，你可以透過指令的方式來呼叫 Copilot 來幫你撰寫程式碼，這樣就不會在檔案中留下註解，你只需要在程式碼頁面按下 ",[63,234,235],{},"Command + I","（Mac）或是 ",[63,238,239],{},"Ctrl + I","（Windows）即可呼叫出 Copilot 視窗，然後你只需要輸入你期望它幫你產出來的內容即可。",[12,242,243],{},[15,244],{"alt":245,"src":246},"Copilot 視窗","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002Fblog\u002Fvscode\u002Fgithub-copilot\u002F%E6%88%AA%E5%9C%96%202024-09-08%2013.59.50.png",[12,248,249],{},"舉例來講，我請 Copilot 幫我做一個 AJAX 行為",[251,252,257],"pre",{"className":253,"code":254,"language":255,"meta":256,"style":256},"language-md shiki shiki-themes github-dark-high-contrast","請幫我用 fetch 來撈取 TodoList API 資料，Url 是 https:\u002F\u002Fjsonplaceholder.typicode.com\u002Ftodos\u002F1， 然後使用 console.log 來輸出結果到 console，請注意 Error 的處理，如果 AJAX 出現錯誤時，請跳出「AJAX 發生錯誤」的訊息。\n","md","",[63,258,259],{"__ignoreMap":256},[260,261,264],"span",{"class":262,"line":263},"line",1,[260,265,254],{"class":266},"sMAXC",[12,268,269],{},[15,270],{"alt":229,"src":271},"https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002Fblog\u002Fvscode\u002Fgithub-copilot\u002FSep-08-2024%2014-04-13.gif",[12,273,274],{},"如果你不滿意它寫的內容，你還可以繼續接續要求它修正，直到你滿意為止",[12,276,277],{},[15,278],{"alt":279,"src":280},"再次修正","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002Fblog\u002Fvscode\u002Fgithub-copilot\u002F%E6%88%AA%E5%9C%96%202024-09-08%2014.07.04.png",[12,282,283],{},"你也可以點一下「下拉」它轉到 Chat 模式，這樣 Copilot 就會變成 Chat 模式，這樣你就可以跟 Copilot 進行對話，讓 Copilot 幫你撰寫程式碼，直到你按下「打勾」為止",[12,285,286],{},[15,287],{"alt":288,"src":289},"Chat - 1","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002Fblog\u002Fvscode\u002Fgithub-copilot\u002F%E6%88%AA%E5%9C%96%202024-09-08%2014.09.19.png",[12,291,292],{},[15,293],{"alt":294,"src":295},"Chat - 2","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002Fblog\u002Fvscode\u002Fgithub-copilot\u002F%E6%88%AA%E5%9C%96%202024-09-08%2014.10.43.png",[161,297,299],{"id":298},"附加檔案請-copilot-幫你撰寫程式碼","附加檔案請 Copilot 幫你撰寫程式碼",[12,301,302],{},"指令模式其實還可以讀取檔案來產生程式碼，例如：你可以讓 Copilot 幫你讀取一個 Markdown 檔案，然後讓它幫你產好全部程式碼。",[12,304,305],{},"舉例我有一個 Markdown 叫做 Prompt.md，裡面的內容是：",[251,307,309],{"className":253,"code":308,"language":255,"meta":256,"style":256},"# 程式碼題詞\n\n請幫我用 fetch 來撈取 TodoList API 資料，Url 是 `https:\u002F\u002Fjsonplaceholder.typicode.com\u002Ftodos\u002F1`， 然後使用 console.log 來輸出結果到 console，請注意 Error 的處理，如果 AJAX 出現錯誤時，請跳出「AJAX 發生錯誤」的訊息。\n\n",[63,310,311,317,324],{"__ignoreMap":256},[260,312,313],{"class":262,"line":263},[260,314,316],{"class":315},"s-VM4","# 程式碼題詞\n",[260,318,320],{"class":262,"line":319},2,[260,321,323],{"emptyLinePlaceholder":322},true,"\n",[260,325,327,330,334],{"class":262,"line":326},3,[260,328,329],{"class":266},"請幫我用 fetch 來撈取 TodoList API 資料，Url 是 ",[260,331,333],{"class":332},"sCcAr","`https:\u002F\u002Fjsonplaceholder.typicode.com\u002Ftodos\u002F1`",[260,335,336],{"class":266},"， 然後使用 console.log 來輸出結果到 console，請注意 Error 的處理，如果 AJAX 出現錯誤時，請跳出「AJAX 發生錯誤」的訊息。\n",[12,338,339,340,236,342,344],{},"然後我在程式碼頁面按下 ",[63,341,235],{},[63,343,239],{},"（Windows）呼叫 Copilot 視窗，然後點附加檔案的圖案，在輸入你要它做的事情，這樣 Copilot 就會讀取 Prompt.md 的內容，然後幫你產生程式碼",[12,346,347],{},[15,348],{"alt":349,"src":350},"讀取檔案產生程式碼","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002Fblog\u002Fvscode\u002Fgithub-copilot\u002F%E6%88%AA%E5%9C%96%202024-09-08%2014.32.58.png",[161,352,354],{"id":353},"選取程式碼讓-copilot-幫你修正調整","選取程式碼讓 Copilot 幫你修正\u002F調整",[12,356,357],{},"假設你有一段程式碼出現 Bug，你可以將那一段程式碼給選取起來，然後呼叫出 Copilot 視窗，請幫它修正",[12,359,360],{},[15,361],{"alt":362,"src":363},"修正程式碼","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002Fblog\u002Fvscode\u002Fgithub-copilot\u002F%E6%88%AA%E5%9C%96%202024-09-08%2014.46.00.png",[161,365,367],{"id":366},"右鍵選單呼叫-copilot","右鍵選單呼叫 Copilot",[12,369,370],{},"選取片段程式碼之後，你可以點擊右鍵找到「Copilot」選項，請它幫你做一些事情",[12,372,373],{},[15,374],{"alt":375,"src":376},"右鍵選單","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002Fblog\u002Fvscode\u002Fgithub-copilot\u002F%E6%88%AA%E5%9C%96%202024-09-08%2014.47.54.png",[12,378,379],{},"例如我想要產生測試程式碼，我就可以選擇「產生測試」，然後 Copilot 就會幫我產生測試程式碼，而且會馬上另外開啟一個檔案給你，並且一次寫完",[12,381,382],{},[15,383],{"alt":384,"src":385},"產生測試","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002Fblog\u002Fvscode\u002Fgithub-copilot\u002F%E6%88%AA%E5%9C%96%202024-09-08%2014.49.30.png",[12,387,388],{},"當然你也可以請它針對專案生成 README.md 也完全 ok，也就是搭配讀取檔案的功能",[12,390,391],{},[15,392],{"alt":393,"src":394},"README.md","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002Fblog\u002Fvscode\u002Fgithub-copilot\u002F%E6%88%AA%E5%9C%96%202024-09-08%2014.55.49.png",[20,396,398,399,402],{"id":397},"copilot-chat-的-指令","Copilot Chat 的 ",[63,400,401],{},"@"," 指令",[12,404,405,406,408],{},"Copilot 其實有內建一些指令，這些指令是以 ",[63,407,401],{}," 開頭的，但這些指令大多都是在 Chat 模式下才能使用，這邊我們來看看一些 Copilot 的指令。",[54,410,411],{},[12,412,413,415],{},[40,414,60],{},"\n這些指令有助於更精準的給予回饋，而非一般的對話唷！",[161,417,419,422],{"id":418},"terminal詢問如何在終端機中執行某些動作",[63,420,421],{},"@terminal","（詢問如何在終端機中執行某些動作）",[12,424,425],{},"這個指令是用來詢問如何在終端機中執行某些動作，例如：我該如何啟動我的專案？",[12,427,428],{},[15,429],{"alt":421,"src":430},"https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002Fblog\u002Fvscode\u002Fgithub-copilot\u002F%E6%88%AA%E5%9C%96%202024-09-08%2015.09.14.png",[12,432,433],{},"或者是該如何用終端機建立檔案",[12,435,436],{},[15,437],{"alt":421,"src":438},"https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002Fblog\u002Fvscode\u002Fgithub-copilot\u002F%E6%88%AA%E5%9C%96%202024-09-08%2015.10.28.png",[12,440,441,442,444],{},"簡單來講，你可以用 ",[63,443,421],{}," 來詢問一些終端機的操作，這個產出來的指令會更精準且符合你的需求產出。",[161,446,448,451],{"id":447},"vscode詢問有關-vs-code-的問題",[63,449,450],{},"@vscode","（詢問有關 VS Code 的問題）",[12,453,454],{},"這個指令是用來詢問有關 VS Code 的問題，例如：我該如何預設讓 CRLF 變成 LF？",[12,456,457],{},[15,458],{"alt":450,"src":459},"https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002Fblog\u002Fvscode\u002Fgithub-copilot\u002F%E6%88%AA%E5%9C%96%202024-09-08%2015.14.28.png",[12,461,462,463,465],{},"透過 ",[63,464,450],{}," 這個指令，你可以快速詢問 VS Code 的問題，直接解決了你在 VSCode 上的一些問題。",[161,467,469,472],{"id":468},"workspace提出有關您工作區的問題",[63,470,471],{},"@workspace","（提出有關您工作區的問題）",[12,474,475,476,479,480,483],{},"這個是 Chat 最強大的功能之一，這個指令是用來詢問有關你的工作區的問題，例如：你可以幫我針對 ",[63,477,478],{},"utils\u002Ftime.js"," 中的 ",[63,481,482],{},"expiresInToMilliseconds"," 生成測試嗎？",[12,485,486,487,489],{},"通常來講 ",[63,488,471],{}," 會跑比較慢，因為它會去掃描你的工作區，然後生成程式碼，同時告知你它參考了哪些檔案",[12,491,492],{},[15,493],{"alt":471,"src":494},"https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002Fblog\u002Fvscode\u002Fgithub-copilot\u002F%E6%88%AA%E5%9C%96%202024-09-08%2015.20.08.png",[54,496,497],{},[12,498,499,501,502,504],{},[40,500,60],{},"\n有時候 ",[63,503,471],{}," 會因為工作區太大而無法參考整份檔案，因為 Token 有一定的限制（此處是指傳給 Copilot 的 Token），所以有時候會無法參考整份檔案，這時候你可以將檔案分割成小檔案，然後再詢問 Copilot。",[20,506,507],{"id":507},"結論",[12,509,510],{},"GitHub Copilot 其實一直都有在優化，而且功能越來越多，只要你能夠掌握一些技巧，你就可以更快速的完成需求，但是還是要注意一件事情，AI 只是輔助你加速開發，實際上產出來的東西還是要自己檢查一遍，這樣才能確保程式碼的品質以及安全性。",[512,513,514],"style",{},"html pre.shiki code .sMAXC, html code.shiki .sMAXC{--shiki-default:#F0F3F6}html .default .shiki span {color: var(--shiki-default);background: var(--shiki-default-bg);font-style: var(--shiki-default-font-style);font-weight: var(--shiki-default-font-weight);text-decoration: var(--shiki-default-text-decoration);}html .shiki span {color: var(--shiki-default);background: var(--shiki-default-bg);font-style: var(--shiki-default-font-style);font-weight: var(--shiki-default-font-weight);text-decoration: var(--shiki-default-text-decoration);}html pre.shiki code .s-VM4, html code.shiki .s-VM4{--shiki-default:#91CBFF;--shiki-default-font-weight:bold}html pre.shiki code .sCcAr, html code.shiki .sCcAr{--shiki-default:#91CBFF}",{"title":256,"searchDepth":319,"depth":319,"links":516},[517,518,519,520,527,536],{"id":22,"depth":319,"text":22},{"id":28,"depth":319,"text":29},{"id":69,"depth":319,"text":70},{"id":135,"depth":319,"text":136,"children":521},[522,523,524,525,526],{"id":163,"depth":326,"text":163},{"id":228,"depth":326,"text":229},{"id":298,"depth":326,"text":299},{"id":353,"depth":326,"text":354},{"id":366,"depth":326,"text":367},{"id":397,"depth":319,"text":528,"children":529},"Copilot Chat 的 @ 指令",[530,532,534],{"id":418,"depth":326,"text":531},"@terminal（詢問如何在終端機中執行某些動作）",{"id":447,"depth":326,"text":533},"@vscode（詢問有關 VS Code 的問題）",{"id":468,"depth":326,"text":535},"@workspace（提出有關您工作區的問題）",{"id":507,"depth":319,"text":507},"VSCode","2024-09-08 13:06:00","zh-Hant",{},"\u002Fvscode\u002Fgithub-copilot","5",{"title":6,"description":25},false,"VSCode\u002FGitHub-Copilot-技巧全攻略不藏私！",[17,547,548],"Visual Studio Code","開發技巧",null,"\u002Fvscode\u002F20240908\u002F3488366595\u002F","cbqbskOQ0jt5EzMlVVLOGYCAT1eupzFeMpQjx1L39xI",{"newer":553,"older":557},{"url":554,"title":555,"date":556},"\u002Fnuxt\u002F20240919\u002F4102603832\u002F","還原專案噴 Cannot find module @rollup\u002Frollup-darwin-arm64 錯誤","2024-09-19 10:08:07",{"url":558,"title":559,"date":560},"\u002Fjavascript\u002F20240727\u002F2019383251\u002F","Vue 與 React 差異在哪？一篇看懂兩大前端框架怎麼選（含面試常見考點）","2024-07-27 16:40:24",[562,567,571],{"url":563,"title":564,"date":565,"readingMinutes":566},"\u002Fvscode\u002F20250424\u002F4258825567\u002F","VSCode 找不到 Git，安裝它或使用 \"git.path\" 設置","2025-04-24 09:52:23","1",{"url":568,"title":569,"date":570,"readingMinutes":566},"\u002Fvscode\u002F20231026\u002F54606935\u002F","VSCode 上 Vue 自訂元件失去高亮","2023-10-26 11:03:07",{"url":572,"title":573,"date":574,"readingMinutes":575},"\u002Fvscode\u002F20230921\u002F1985180173\u002F","Visual Studio Code 自訂折疊區塊","2023-09-21 09:43:55","2",1784013104541]